<lb n="0910b08"/><head>No. 1467</head>
<lb n="0910b09"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/>◎<note n="0910006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此經聖本大異今附卷末，〔佛說〕－【聖乙】</note><note n="0910006" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>此經聖本大異今附卷末，〔佛說〕－【聖乙】</note>佛說犯戒罪<note n="0910007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔報〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔報〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910007"><lem>報</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>輕重經</juan>
<lb n="0910b10"/>
<lb n="0910b11"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0910008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後漢安息三藏安世高譯＝出在目蓮問毘尼經後秦安世高譯【聖乙】</note><app n="0910008"><lem>後漢安息三藏安世高<note n="0910009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譯＋（漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非）夾註【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯＋（漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910009"><lem>譯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">譯<note place="inline">漢隋唐錄並云世高所譯恐非</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">出在目蓮問毘尼經後秦安世高譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0910b12"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛住王舍城迦蘭陀竹園。爾
<lb n="0910b13"/>時尊者<note n="0910010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目連＝大目犍連【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">目連＝大目犍連【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910010"><lem>目連</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">大目犍連</rdg></app>。晡<note n="0910011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【宮】</note><app n="0910011"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>從禪定覺。往至<note n="0910012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世尊〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910012"><lem>世尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0910b14"/><note n="0910013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋所【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛）＋所【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910013"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">佛所</rdg></app>。頭面禮足<note n="0910014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00230;住一面〕－【宮】</note><app n="0910014"><lem>&CB00230;<note n="0910015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝坐【三】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝坐【宋】【元】【明】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910015"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">坐</rdg></app>一面</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0910016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時尊者大目連＝合掌恭敬而【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時尊者大目連＝合掌恭敬而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910016"><lem>時尊者大目連</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">合掌恭敬而</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0910b15"/>白佛言。世尊。意有所疑今欲請問。<note n="0910017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910017"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願聽
<lb n="0910b16"/>許。佛告目連。<note n="0910018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聽＝恣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽＝恣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910018"><lem>聽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恣</rdg></app>汝所問。當為汝說。目連。即
<lb n="0910b17"/>白佛言。世尊。若比丘比丘尼。無慚愧<note n="0910019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【宮】</note><app n="0910019"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>輕
<lb n="0910b18"/>慢佛語。犯眾學戒。如是犯波羅提提舍尼。波
<lb n="0910b19"/><note n="0910020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝逸【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜＝逸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910020"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">逸</rdg></app>提。偷蘭遮。僧伽婆尸沙。<note n="0910021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（犯）＋波【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（犯）＋波【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910021"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犯波</rdg></app>羅夷。得幾
<lb n="0910b20"/><note n="0910022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔所〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910022"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不饒益罪。<anchor id="fxT24p0910b01"/>唯願解說。佛告目連。諦聽諦
<lb n="0910b21"/>聽。<note n="0910023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝今【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝今【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910023"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">今</rdg></app>為汝說。若比丘比丘尼無慚無愧。輕
<lb n="0910b22"/>慢佛<note n="0910024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝說【聖乙】</note><app n="0910024"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>犯眾學戒。如四天王<note n="0910025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔天〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910025"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>壽五百歲。
<lb n="0910b23"/>墮泥犁中。於人間數九百千歲。<note n="0910026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛告＝復次【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0910026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛告＝復次【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0910026"><lem>佛告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復次</rdg></app>目連。
<lb n="0910b24"/><note n="0910027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（若）＋無慚【三】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><note n="0910027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（若）＋無慚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><app n="0910027"><lem>無慚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">若無慚</rdg></app><note n="0910028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><note n="0910028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔無〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note><app n="0910028"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>愧輕慢佛語。犯波羅提提舍尼。如
<lb n="0910b25"/>三十三天壽<note n="0910029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910029"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>千歲。墮泥<corr sic="梨">犁</corr>中。於人間數三
<lb n="0910b26"/>億六十千歲。<anchor id="fxT24p0910b02"/>佛告目連。<anchor id="fxT24p0910b03"/>無慚<anchor id="fxT24p0910b04"/>無愧輕慢佛
<lb n="0910b27"/>語。犯波<note n="0910030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝逸【聖乙】</note><app n="0910030"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">逸</rdg></app>提。如<note n="0910031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＝焰【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜＝焰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910031"><lem>夜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">焰</rdg></app>摩天壽二千歲。墮泥犁
<lb n="0910b28"/>中。於人間數二<note n="0910032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">十＋（四）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十＋（四）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910032"><lem>十</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">十四</rdg></app>億四十千歲<anchor id="fxT24p0910b05"/>佛告目連。
<lb n="0910b29"/><anchor id="fxT24p0910b06"/>無慚<anchor id="fxT24p0910b07"/>無愧輕慢佛語。犯偷蘭遮。如兜率天
<pb ed="T" id="T24.1467a.0910c" n="0910c"/>
<lb n="0910c01"/>壽四千歲。墮泥犁中。於人間數。五十億六十
<lb n="0910c02"/>千歲。<anchor id="fxT24p0910c01"/>佛告目連。<anchor id="fxT24p0910c02"/>無慚<anchor id="fxT24p0910c03"/>無愧輕慢佛語。犯
<lb n="0910c03"/>僧伽婆尸沙。如不憍樂天壽八千歲。墮泥犁
<lb n="0910c04"/>中。於人間數。二百三十億四十千歲。<anchor id="fxT24p0910c04"/>佛告
<lb n="0910c05"/>目連。<anchor id="fxT24p0910c05"/>無慚<anchor id="fxT24p0910c06"/>無愧輕慢佛語。犯波羅夷。如他
<lb n="0910c06"/>化自在天壽十六千歲。墮泥犁中。於人間數。
<lb n="0910c07"/>九百二十一億<note n="0910033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＝九【聖乙】</note><app n="0910033"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">九</rdg></app>十千歲。<note n="0910034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔時〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910034"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>尊者目連聞
<lb n="0910c08"/>佛所說歡喜奉行</p>
<lb n="0910c09"/><p>爾時<note n="0910035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔尊者〕－【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note><note n="0910035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔尊者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】</note><app n="0910035"><lem>尊者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>目連。即說偈言</p>
<lb n="0910c10"/><lg><l>因緣輕慢故</l><l>命終墮惡道</l>
<lb n="0910c11"/><l>因緣修善<note n="0910036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝故【宮】</note><app n="0910036"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app></l><l>於此生天上</l>
<lb n="0910c12"/><l>緣斯<note n="0910037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">修福業＝善業故【聖乙】</note><app n="0910037"><lem>修<note n="0910038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">福＝善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910038"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>業</lem><rdg wit="【聖乙】" resp="Taisho">善業故</rdg></app></l><l>離惡得解脫</l>
<lb n="0910c13"/><l>不善觀因緣</l><l>身壞<note n="0910039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入惡道＝墮惡趣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入惡道＝墮惡趣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910039"><lem>入惡道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">墮惡趣</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0910c14"/><note n="0910040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（比丘…佛））二十四句百二十字＝（（為福受樂報所欲皆自然超逾生死流上家之涅槃若人為福者天神自然護所願皆疾成眾魔莫能壞））五言八句四十字【聖乙】</note><note n="0910040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（比丘…佛））百二十字＝（（為福受樂報所欲皆自然超逾生死流上家之涅槃若人為福者天神自然護所願皆疾成眾魔莫能壞））四十字【聖乙】</note><app n="0910040" word-count="120"><lem><l>比丘謹慎樂</l><l>放逸多憂譴</l>
<lb n="0910c15"/><l>變諍小致大</l><l>積惡入火<note n="0910041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01853;＝焚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0910041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB01853;＝焚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0910041"><lem>&CB01853;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">焚</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0910c16"/><l>持戒福致喜</l><l>破戒有懼心</l>
<lb n="0910c17"/><l>永斷三界漏</l><l>爾乃得涅槃</l>
